---
title: Pork Sausage & Creamy Tomato Pasta with Soffritto & Parmesan
description: Who here loves a saucy spaghetti night, but we’ve had spaghetti so many ways how can we add a special touch? Pork sausages are coming to the rescue to make a delicious pork sausage sauce. Spaghetti night is back in business.

*We've replaced the
spaghetti in this recipe
with fettuccine due
to local ingredient
availability. It'll be just
as delicious, just follow
your recipe card!*
